    h4#Business School of Business
    p.lead
      | The School of Business is a large organization with MBA, IMBA, and GSB in the MBA programs, and BA programs in the School of Business Administration and Global Business Administration. Many executives, professors, and management specialists are emerging, especially since the Samsung Group took over the foundation 20 years ago, it has achieved remarkable growth in many ways. Sungkyunkwan University was ranked as the first comprehensive private university in Korea by the international evaluation agency (The Times, US News & Report, etc.) and the domestic evaluation agency (Joongang Daily). In Financial Times, For the first time in a row, it is Korea's number one and is introducing it as an institution with a global MBA program.
